# === Monorepo .gitignore for multi-tenant-monitoring ===
# All services share these patterns. Per-service .gitignore files
# are for local IDE convenience only and are not committed.

# Maven/Java build artifacts (all services)
**/HELP.md
**/target/
**/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/

# IDE files (all services)
**/.apt_generated/
**/.classpath
**/.factorypath
**/.project
**/.settings/
**/.springBeans/
**/.sts4-cache/
**/*.iws
**/*.iml
**/*.ipr
**/.idea/

# VS Code
**/.vscode/

# Editor/Tool
**/nbproject/private/
**/nbbuild/
**/dist/
**/nbdist/
**/.nb-gradle/
**/build/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

# Environment configs (all services)
**/src/main/resources/application.properties

# Claude Code
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
